o come unto the knowledge of the truth.","year":65},{"id":"recZRYyNMewA1zLIE","ref":"1Tim.2.5","text":"For there is one God, and one mediator between God and men, the man Christ Jesus;","year":65},{"id":"recUqHQMZIJph5HWM","ref":"1Tim.2.6","text":"Who gave himself a ransom for all, to be testified in due time.","year":65},{"id":"recFOaTlAbmQcrjcJ","ref":"1Tim.2.7","text":"Whereunto I am ordained a preacher, and an apostle, (I speak the truth in Christ, and lie not;) a teacher of the Gentiles in faith and verity.","year":65},{"id":"reccK6rerHCqZKWc5","ref":"1Tim.2.8","text":"I will therefore that men pray every where, lifting up holy hands, without wrath and doubting.","year":65}]}
